embed.description: News about the bot. To check please do `/news get` or `<prefix>news`

<:new:736926339113680976> Bot Hosting Upgraded, moved away from self-hosting on raspberry pi to KVM VPS hosting. If you like the bot, please support it, you can check the link at the [site](https://redhusky.hostingerapp.com/muzzledfox/).
